qx|d 5,Example Deal 5|

st||sv||ha||
rh||ah|Deal 5|ah|Suit Preference|ah|Signals|

md|3skq983hk3dkqcq972,sa65h7djt86cjt865,sjt74hjqt92da3ca3|
