cs|2|at|^-{ Some players use suit preference signals when a honor card is led in a side suit 
 against a trump contract and the dummy has a singleton or void in that suit. }
^-
|
pg| ***** 219 ***** |


cs|3|at|^-{ Some players use suit preference signals when both their
  attitude and their count in a given suit is already known. }
^-
|
pg| ***** 220 ***** |


cs|1|at|^-{ Some players use suit preference signals in the trump suit itself. }
^-
|
