nt|^b@2^z@3|n#|5|at|Here are 2 concepts that relate to the philosophy of all types of signals and which types of signals should be used in various defensive situations:

|
pg| ***** 224 ***** |


cs|1|at|^-{ One of the basic premises of signaling is that cards that are not relevant in terms of 
