at|Signaling is all about helping your partner to defend better. When you are thinking about making a signal you should try to think about the deal from your partner's point of view and try to give him the information that you think he will need the most. The guidelines that we have established for when to use each type of signal are very sound and they will usually work for you, but remember they are still guidelines - not rules!

